statements.sql: select "c"."id", "idnumber", "summary", "summaryformat", "startdate", "enddate", "shortname", "fullname", "category", "visible", "ctx"."id" as "ctxid", "ctx"."path" as "ctxpath", "ctx"."depth" as "ctxdepth", "ctx"."contextlevel" as "ctxlevel", "ctx"."instanceid" as "ctxinstance", "ctx"."locked" as "ctxlocked" from "mdl_course" as "c" inner join "mdl_context" as "ctx" on "ctx"."instanceid" = "c"."id" and "ctx"."contextlevel" = '50' inner join "mdl_user_lastaccess" as "ul" on "ul"."courseid" = "c"."id" left join "mdl_favourite" as "fav" on "fav"."itemid" = "ul"."courseid" and "fav"."component" = 'core_course' and "fav"."itemtype" = 'courses' and "fav"."userid" = 7 left join "mdl_enrol" as "eg" on "eg"."courseid" = "c"."id" and "eg"."status" = '0' and "eg"."enrol" = 'guest' where "ul"."userid" = 7 and "c"."visible" = 1 and ("eg"."id" is not null or exists (select "e"."id" from "mdl_enrol" as "e" inner join "mdl_user_enrolments" as "ue" on "ue"."enrolid" = "e"."id" where "e"."courseid" = "c"."id" and "e"."status" = '0' and "ue"."status" = '0' and "ue"."userid" = 58854 and "ue"."timestart" < 1739930345 and ("ue"."timeend" = 0 or "ue"."timeend" > 1739930345))) order by "timeaccess" desc limit 2

select "c"."id" as "courseid", "c"."fullname", COUNT(DISTINCT cmc.id) as completed_activities, COUNT(DISTINCT cm.id) as total_activities, ROUND((COUNT(DISTINCT cmc.id) * 100.0) / COUNT(DISTINCT cm.id), 2) as completion_percentage from "mdl_course" as "c" inner join "mdl_course_modules" as "cm" on "cm"."course" = "c"."id" left join "mdl_course_modules_completion" as "cmc" on "cmc"."coursemoduleid" = "cm"."id" and "cmc"."userid" = 58854 and "cmc"."completionstate" = 1 where "cm"."completion" > 0 and 0 = 1 group by "c"."id", "c"."fullname"

select "c"."id", "c"."category", "c"."sortorder", "c"."shortname", "c"."fullname", "c"."idnumber", "c"."startdate", "c"."visible", "c"."groupmode", "c"."groupmodeforce", "c"."cacherev", "c"."summary", "c"."summaryformat", "c"."enddate", "ctx"."id" as "ctxid", "ctx"."path" as "ctxpath", "ctx"."depth" as "ctxdepth", "ctx"."contextlevel" as "ctxlevel", "ctx"."instanceid" as "ctxinstance", "ctx"."locked" as "ctxlocked" from "mdl_course" as "c" inner join (select distinct "e"."courseid" from "mdl_enrol" as "e" inner join "mdl_user_enrolments" as "ue" on "ue"."enrolid" = "e"."id" and "ue"."userid" = 58854 and "ue"."status" = 0 and "e"."status" = 0 and "ue"."timestart" <= 1739930345 and ("ue"."timeend" = 0 or "ue"."timeend" > 1739930345)) as "en" on "en"."courseid" = "c"."id" left join "mdl_context" as "ctx" on "ctx"."instanceid" = "c"."id" and "ctx"."contextlevel" = 50 where "c"."id" <> 1 order by "c"."visible" desc, "c"."fullname" asc
